Package: dockttier-plugin
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: dockttier maintainers <maintainers@dockttier.dev>
Depends: docker-ce | docker.io
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Docker CLI output prettifier
 dockttier enhances Docker command output with rich terminal formatting.
 Installs as a transparent proxy — use docker commands exactly as normal.
 The real docker binary is never modified; dockttier simply runs in front of
 it and re-renders its output. Disable per-command with DOCKTTIER_DISABLE=1.
